sequenceDiagram
  actor Eng as Engineer
  participant AI as AI agent
  participant MCP as rf-mcp
  participant RF as Live RF context
  Eng->>AI: Describe the test in plain words
  AI->>MCP: analyze_scenario + recommend_libraries
  MCP-->>AI: A plan and the right libraries
  loop Build it step by step
    AI->>MCP: execute_step
    MCP->>RF: Run the keyword in a live context
    RF-->>MCP: Result, page source, state
    MCP-->>AI: Feedback for the next move
  end
  AI->>MCP: build_test_suite
  MCP-->>Eng: A clean .robot suite
